426
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:36,240
Suanmaeul Underground, Front Mie Daehan, SD Bombi

427
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:40,100
Apa-apaan ini? Kenapa dia tidak membalas pesannya?

428
00:30:40,100 --> 00:30:42,950
